==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thallic
<hw>Thal"lic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of
or pertaining to thallium; derived from, or containing, thallium;
specifically, designating those compounds in which the element has a
higher valence as contrasted with the <contr>thallous</contr> compounds;
<as>as, <ex>thallic</ex> oxide</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thalline</ent>⟦br⟧
